name: Cooky
description:
My Daughtr said:
If you are a fan of BTS, of course you are familiar with Jungkook who likes work-outs. So does his character, Cooky. Even though it's pink, Cooky is not someone who just relaxes to beautify himself. The pink rabbit made by the maknae, Jungkook, is very diligent in doing work out because he dreams of having a muscular body. The hallmark of Cooky is to have unique eyebrows and a heart-shaped buttocks. Very hardworking and cute bunny, right? Every day that Cooky does to fulfill his dream is a 120-minute run, 400 push-ups, muscle checks and 100 minutes of eyebrow drawing. Excited...
